            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;This is a very handy set of methods for manipulating arrays stored in localStorage or sessionStorage, and deserves much more credit than it&apos;s attracted. @Andy Lorenz Thanks for taking the time to share!&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/1200867/velojet&quot; title=&quot;838 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Velojet&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment78542239_23516713&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2017-08-21 08:19:13Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Aug 21, 2017 at 8:19&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
